Jackie Sardou https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jackie_Sardou 0 Jackie Sardou (7 April 1919 – 2 April 1998) was a French actress. She was born Jacqueline Labbé in Paris, and married Fernand Sardou, a singer. She is the mother of singer Michel Sardou; and grandmother of Romain Sardou, an author and of Davy Sardou an actor. She died in 1998 five days before her 79th birthday. Jackie_Sardou ( 7_April_1919 – 2_April_1998 ) was a_French_actress .
